Alloran, remember how we were gonna have Orion meet Prowl?

::Cledar/Forrior/Rixer/Blyer::

Cledar, Forrior, Rixer, and Blyer approach the group of Maximals, Cledar stepping forward.

"Hello," he says, "I'm Cledar and this is my group. We're new here. Who are all of you?"
